high_descs: Turn left towards bed and desk
Pick up white pen on desk
Turn 90 degrees, and go towards desk across the room
Directly place pen into metal bowl
Pick up bowl with pen in it
Turn left towards the desk
Place bowl with pen in it onto desk.
anns.task_desc: Find pen on desk, put into metal bowl, place onto desk.

high_descs: Turn around to the table
Grab the pen on the table
Turn around and walk to the cabinet with two bowls on it
Put the pen in the bowl on the right
Take the bowl on the right
Turn right to the white table
Put the bowl down on the table
anns.task_desc: Put the pen from the table to the bowl on the right, move the bowl to the white table

high_descs: Move right to the end table with the lamp and the alarm clock.
Pick up the ink pen that is on the top.
Turn to the left and stop at the dresser in front of you with the silver bowls
Place the pen in the silver bowl on the right.
Pick up the bowl and the pen that are on the flat surface.
Turn to the left to the desk with the laptop.
Place the bowl on the desk next to the laptop computer.
